                        浏览次数：<span id="spVisitCountd88d6be3-e933-433f-a537-4c4ee45a5afe"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="divContent" class="divContent">
                        <p style="color:#666666;font-family:Arial;" align="center"> <span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;"><img src="http://file.szmuseum.com:8022/文章富文本文件/image/20150615/20150615165043_3475.jpg" alt=""><br> </span></span> </p> <p style="color:#666666;font-family:Arial;" align="center"> <span style="color:#000000;"><span style="color:#000000;">高19．2厘米</span></span> </p> <p style="color:#666666;font-family:Arial;" align="left"> <span><span><br> <span style="color:#000000;">   1956年在苏州虎丘云岩寺塔第三层发现。螺髻，双耳垂肩，身着袒右袈裟，结跏趺坐于圆形蒲团座上，背而出一环纽，未见背光。</span></span></span> </p>
                    </div>
